Difficulty:Rare

Description:Test puzzle for replaying a targeted untap mana loop from the commander combo list: Staff of Domination plus Selvala, Heart of the Wilds. Colossal Dreadmaw makes Selvala produce six mana. Record one cycle that taps Selvala for mana, uses Staff of Domination to untap Selvala, then untaps Staff. Repeat to build enough red mana, then cast Banefire targeting the opponent.

